# CareerMentor.AI - Next-Gen Career Platform (MERN + AI)

## ğŸš€ Project Overview

**CareerMentor.AI** is an advanced, AI-driven career development platform built on the MERN stack. It empowers students and job seekers with intelligent tools for resume analysis, interview preparation, job tracking, and community engagement. Leveraging the Perplexity API for AI features, CareerMentor.AI delivers actionable insights and a seamless, modern user experience.

---

## ğŸ§© Core Technologies

- **Frontend:** React.js, Tailwind CSS, React Router, Framer Motion
- **Backend:** Node.js, Express.js
- **Database:** MongoDB Atlas (Cloud)
- **Authentication:** JWT (JSON Web Tokens)
- **AI Integration:** Perplexity API (for Resume Feedback, AI Q&A, Mock Interviews)
- **Voice Input:** Web Speech API or Perplexity (if supported)

