---

## ğŸŒŸ What CareerMentor.AI Can Do

- **AI Resume Optimizer:** Instantly analyze your resume and receive tailored, actionable feedback for ATS optimization, keyword density, and formattingâ€”powered by Perplexity AI.
- **Smart Interview Coach:** Practice with AI-driven mock interviews for any job role, with real-time, personalized feedback and coaching.
- **Career Roadmap AI:** Get a dynamic, personalized learning and career advancement path, including skills assessment and milestone tracking.
- **24/7 AI Career Mentor:** Access expert career advice and answers to your questions anytime, anywhere.
- **Smart Job Tracker:** Organize and track your job applications, receive analytics, reminders, and market insights.
- **Community Forum:** Post questions, share experiences, and get AI-powered suggestions and peer support.
- **Voice Input:** Use voice to interact with AI features (where supported).
- **Secure User Authentication:** Register, log in, and manage your personalized dashboard securely.
- **Animated, Responsive UI:** Enjoy a visually stunning, interactive experience on any device.

---

## âœ¨ Key Features

1. **Authentication:** Secure JWT-based login and registration, with role-based access (Admin, User).
2. **Dashboard:** Centralized overview of your job applications, interview tasks, and AI feedback.
3. **Job Tracker:** Effortlessly manage your job applications with status tracking (Applied, Interviewed, Rejected, Hired).
4. **Interview Prep:** Create, edit, and practice company-specific Q&A, with revision tools and AI suggestions.
5. **Resume Analyzer:** Upload your PDF resume and receive in-depth analysis and improvement tips from Perplexity AI.
6. **Community Forum:** Engage with peers, post doubts, and receive AI-generated suggestions and answers.
7. **AI Mock Interviews:** Select topics (e.g., DSA, React) and experience realistic, AI-evaluated mock interviews.
8. **Voice Interaction:** Use voice input for hands-free AI engagement (where available).
9. **Modern UI/UX:** Animated, gradient-rich, and responsive design for an engaging user journey.

---

## ğŸ”— API & Tools

- **Perplexity API:**
  - [https://www.perplexity.ai/](https://www.perplexity.ai/)
  - Used for all AI-powered features (resume feedback, Q&A, mock interviews, etc.)
- **Web Speech API:**
  - [MDN Docs](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Speech_API)
  - Enables browser-based voice input.
- **PDF Parsing:**
  - Library: `pdf-parse` ([GitHub](https://github.com/modesty/pdf-parse))
- **Deployment:**
  - **Frontend:** [Netlify](https://www.netlify.com/)
  - **Backend:** [Render](https://render.com/)
  - **Database:** [MongoDB Atlas](https://www.mongodb.com/cloud/atlas/register)

